### Recommendation Accuracy — 1 Correction Made

**HubSpot Ireland Limited** (Row 160, Col 5): `Terminate` → **`Consolidate`**

> **Rule:** "If two vendors serve the same function, at least one must be Consolidate."
> HubSpot ($32K, CRM/marketing automation) is a functional duplicate of Salesforce ($3.1M, CRM). Salesforce is correctly classified as Optimize. HubSpot's classification must be Consolidate — not Terminate — to signal intentional migration of its users/seats into the preferred Salesforce contract rather than simply abandoning the tool.

